DESCRIPTION:We've got a pretty nice weekend coming up considering it is Nov
 ember.  Saturday we'll be reliving the memories/horrors of Blayne & Taylor'
 s Everesting Adventure. It's certainly a tough route\, but some really nice
  roads!  Plenty of drop off points along the way for anyone wanting to go s
 horter.  Sunday is back in the 60's!!\n\nSat: https://www.strava.com/routes
 /2891333062033705644\n\n*All routes created by Ride Coordinator Kevin Hays.
LAST-MODIFIED:20211119T212158Z
LOCATION:Sample Gates\, E Kirkwood Ave & S Indiana Ave\, Bloomington\, IN 4
 7405\, USA
SEQUENCE:4
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Saturday Training Ride
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
